edu.asu.ying.mapreduce.rpc.messaging

Class ElementMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.asu.ying.mapreduce.rpc.messaging.MessageBase
      • edu.asu.ying.mapreduce.rpc.messaging.ElementMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message, TableMessage, Distributable, java.io.Serializable

    public final class ElementMessage
extends MessageBase
implements TableMessage
    ElementMessage objects carry requests for elements from a ServerTableProxy to a data source and carry the Element back to the requesting proxy.

    This enables ServerTableProxy to transparently link a ServerTable to any data source that responds to requests for elements.
